{"tid":2060083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中學校長會主席：學校依排好多野做，教育局不要再發信","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T16:14:04.000Z","uid":5195,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"07c0f56c6a1e706ec7eb9fb9ea3075d90e46abb5","tid":2060083,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄去信全港中小學校長，要求學校禁止師生參與反對港區國安法罷工罷課。中學校長會主席鄧振強在電台節目表示，過往較少老師透過請事假參加罷課，認為學生復課後面對學習壓力，學校有好多實務工作，希望局方不要再向學校發信。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，學校過去面對不少挑戰及危機，校長教師已經處變不驚，當港區國安法有具體條文，校方亦舉辦有意義教育活動，解答學生疑難。<br />\n<br />\n資助小學校長會名譽主席張勇邦則認為，局方信件令校方有依據向老師家長解釋，避免出現誤解及矛盾，因此感到更安心。"},{"pid":"cca83172f4d67c6d00a44696c315d4b528c614e7","tid":2060083,"uid":60924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪再煩住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2ef7da3d5f22ab9ead81eabdef83a279cabbbe","tid":2060083,"uid":39974,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"校長：煩少陣啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"a3f77fc802684a8305c45b10601d66046eaeb262","tid":2060083,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"港共唔比人屌唔知自己柒"},{"pid":"7226a99058332371d345a37b5f753916499b5fd1","tid":2060083,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"屌 好撚煩呀"},{"pid":"713a8c494348ccd5d79a87cca5944c1fd4588e2f","tid":2060083,"uid":168124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"企開d la . DLLM"},{"pid":"86eb13681be5913bbf8121d03ec96330c23d8975","tid":2060083,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"企開d啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"6ddbf7e715703cb2c96c4e220d62359a6e7c1495","tid":2060083,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"